[/2]
	*GLYPH OF LUIN
	
	cr. Vanargand
	dt. Primeval Era*
	@Glyph of Luin: Sword@
	$Glyphs/Luin Sword.png$
	#Luin manifests itself as a sword at will. Once bound to a host, it will remain with the Trueflesh for the rest of their existence. 
	
